ass=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53875edb0746c6648e033f2b597751207cb911ed","tid":2058674,"uid":33743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"587c22331c9d375d75119099f2dc2cf410ffd181","tid":2058674,"uid":300782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"774b8aca3c2f019059fc502b61e546dc7ba1b9c0","tid":2058674,"uid":33743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1fae9441e59a4f81a185978bea301968f28b9469","tid":2058674,"uid":300782,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T11:05:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T11:29:21.000Z","msg":"唔想支那加大持股你係講緊政府定作者定太古<br />\n最尾果條問題你想imply 乜？<br />\n<br />\nFollow 唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T13:05:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T16:01:25.000Z","msg":"如果優先股果19.5bn再加bridge loan果7.8bn 全數用供股形式做<br />\n基本上要1供2先籌夠旗<br />\n唔計國航，太古同qatar各自拎175億同39億 CASH 出黎似乎唔可行? 太古2019年尾cash and cash equivalent 得213億, qatar 更加自身難保 仲未計要有ibank幫你underwrite 街貨唔供果堆..<br />\n要所有股東齊齊夾夠錢頂落去唔太可行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當然講到尾可以話私人企業出得黎行預左會有倒閉風險有嚴峻生意環境，股東有責任自救，救唔到未執笠　但點解外國政府都要救當地嘅航空業呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb63117e1f6f648ec8bc975afc86b4437b9e011c","tid":2058674,"uid":175930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T16:10:08.000Z","msg":"我反而想問 港航呢？<br />\nam I a joke to you.jpg <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d072f78cf924ba5575c968e2f514d7d1927ee25","tid":2058674,"uid":33743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bb63117e1f6f648ec8bc975afc86b4437b9e011c","tid":2058674,"uid":175930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T16:10:08.000Z","msg":"我反而想問 港航呢？<br />\nam I a joke to you.jpg <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T16:51:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當日記招都有記問條好問題 就係會唔會對HKA唔公平 冇一個level playing field 德國漢莎bailout Ryanair都有走出黎投訴<br />\n<br />\n不過望下HKA個問題係本身未有武肺已經真正經營不善, 海航本身自己都笠笠亂, 我諗政府救佢 應該比人屌得仲勁"},{"pid":"47db2ed81c64cf9479ff27a232532472bb3b6575","tid":2058674,"uid":33743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T23:54:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c4c21e779ed5d89a2e421a88963b40763da5f1f","tid":2058674,"uid":33743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T05:16:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}